<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹第二天醒来的时候，雨已经停了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳下床，期待能够见到杰佩托。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他只看到了蓝色小仙女。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想成为一个真正的男孩儿吗？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”匹诺曹兴奋地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想救杰佩托吗？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就仔细听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>想要成为一个真正的男孩儿，你必须听爸爸的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是首先，你必须救他。你通过尊重他来救他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不明白。他不在这里我怎么尊重他？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹不解地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须尊重他的愿望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托想让你做什么？”蓝色小仙女问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他想让我上学。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你必须上学去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可以和我一起住，每天在村庄里学习。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要你尊重他，你就能救他。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹听到这些话，很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不想上学。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他想救他的爸爸。于是匹诺曹答应了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹变成了学校里最棒的学生。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老师对他非常满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，有些学生对匹诺曹很刻薄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天放学后，几个男孩儿在回家路上跟着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个木头脑袋如何能变得聪明呢？”一个男孩儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把它做成书架！”另一个男孩儿说。所有的男孩儿都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“匹诺曹长大后会变成什么？”第一个男孩儿问其他人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个小木头男孩儿！”他们回答。然后他们又笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很聪明。总有一天，我会变成一个真正的男孩儿！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是吗？好吧，如果你现在就能证明你很聪明，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那么今天你就可以变成一个真正的男孩儿。”一个男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这是什么意思？”匹诺曹问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，如果你能做真正的男孩儿做的事情，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那你就是一个真正的男孩儿，对吧？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，应该是。”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘如果我能成为一个真正的男孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我就可以尽快救我的爸爸了。’他心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能做任何你们能做的事情！”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会让你们看到我是一个真正的男孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是吗？今天，我们要逃到天堂去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你是一个真正的男孩儿，你就跟我们来。”一个男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天堂是什么？”匹诺曹问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是一个真正的男孩儿们玩耍的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那里永远不用工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每顿都有甜点。每一个人都很富有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹觉得这听起来很不错。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以他跟着男孩儿们走到村庄的尽头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这里，他们看到了一辆坐满男孩儿的马车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那辆马车被穿着衣服，看起来很不高兴的驴拉着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是男孩儿们没有注意到他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们跳上了马车，前往小岛的尽头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到了，小伙子们！”马车师傅喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这艘船前往天堂，一个每天都是假期的地方，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们永远都不用工作。在船坐满之前快上船吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹和男孩儿们跑向那艘船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹看到很多驴从船上走了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他并没有觉得奇怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想成为一个真正的男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想救他的爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在天堂，这两件事他都可以做到，还不用工作！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
